PrecisAppointment of JESSE FLIS, of Etobicoke, Ontario, as Chairman of the Canadian Section of the Permanent Joint Board on Defence, Canada-United States, for a term of one year, in the place of Patrick Crofton; and request that Jesse Flis, Member of Parliament for the electoral district of Parkdale--High Park, do undertake such travel as may be necessary for the purposes of the above appointment.
